    public class OptionalFieldInput<I>
extends ParseAbstractInput<java.lang.String>
implements ListInput<java.lang.String,I>
    Select a field from an option map that does not already exist in a Repository. The Value of this input is the field name. This is also an ItemInput and will return the corresponding element from the option map as the Item.
